name: Nordic Style All-in-1 Candle Holder, Sage, Incense & Palo Santo Burner
description:
What's Special About These Handmade Retro Ceramic Candle Holders
Featuring a UFO shape, these retro ceramic candle holders would give a candle a retro, charming base and take your table setting to the next level with retro flair. Thoughtfully handcrafted by skill artisans, these retro candle holders come with ring-shape handles, making it easy to carry the candles around
